Package triviaMaze.room

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IRoomLink
    The interface which represents links between rooms which can contain the state that they have.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IRoom
    The interface corresponding to a room within the maze
    LinkedRoom
    An IRoom implementation that has four directional IRoomLinks which store the state of those links and form a maze structure when interconnected
    RoomLink
    An implementation of IRoomLink which holds the state between rooms
